new york state coordinator of aids research and donald s goldman 
a livingston nj attorney 
also dr june osborn dean of the school of public health at 
the university of michigan harry dalton a yale university law 
professor dr charles konigsbert a kansas state health official 
and eunice diaz director of community affairs at white memorial 
medical center in los angeles 
the commission members will select their own chairman 
