said he will propose funding production of only two bombers in 1990 
and 1991 when the administration wants eight bombers his 
amendment would meet the full request for research and development 
work over that period 
he called his amendment a cold turkey fence of the procurement 
money until congress acts again 
aspin said his plan shuts down the program but it gives the 
administration a chance to come up with another program thats 
politically more acceptable financially 
