where the novelist spent a significant portion of his life 
born in oak park in 1899 hemingway lived in the western chicago 
suburb until he was 18 he committed suicide in 1961 at the age of 
61 
ive been sitting here wondering if ernest was alive if he 
would be here today said ae hotchner author of papa 
hemingway and one of hemingways close friends 
yes i think he would be here for all thats been said about 
his feelings for oak park hotchner said it is deeply 
ingrained in him he would have made a lousy speech but he would 
have been moved 
