undone by statute on our side we have just as many distinguished 
lawyers who say that a statute will work edwards told bork 
the former appeals judge smiled 
all of the people who might have been hired to challenge that 
statute have now testified that its constutitional he said 
so i suppose the statute might stand for that reason 
the court ruled 54 that burning the flag is a constitutionally 
