redrawn so as to flatly forbid desecration without mentioning that 
flag burning is offensive to others which is what the texas law 
said 
bork says that wont suffice 
on the other side of the debate stood an old foe laurence h 
tribe a constitutional lawyer who testified against borks supreme 
