futures trading commission which regulates the futures markets of 
a soybean selloff order issued last week by the cbot 
we are extremely concerned about the effects which recent 
events have had on agricultural producers and small investors 
the senators wrote in a letter to cftc chairwoman wendy gramm 
furthermore these events raise important questions about whether 
adequate safeguards are in place to prevent unwarranted emergency 
actions 
