signed by several others including sens rudy boschwitz rminn 
mitch mcconnell rky and robert kerry dneb they serve on the 
senate agriculture committee which oversees the futures markets 
and the regulatory agency 
the lawmakers asked the cftc for a full disclosure of the events 
during the last several months that led up to the emergency order 
including identification of all traders holding positions larger 
than 1 million bushels of soybeans during may june and july 
the order by the board forced some traders to sell off part of 
their holdings in july soybeans and was viewed as an effort to 
break an attempt by a foreign firm to corner the market 
soybean futures prices dropped sharply as a result of the order 
ferruzzi spa an italian agricultural and financial firm 
reportedly had contracts to take delivery on 23 million bushels of 
soybeans this month when there were only about 12 million bushels 
in locations for easy delivery to meet those commitments a move by 
the grain trader to take delivery on its contracts could have 
sharply increased soybean prices company officials have denied any 
attempt to corner the market however 
