easterns flight schedule will not be as large as originally 
announced but they maintained that the smaller expansion is not a 
sign that the rebuilding program is faltering 
the airline originally promised to have 390 flights a day by 
aug 1 but it said this week some reductions may be necessary 
before the strike march 4 eastern had about 1100 daily flights 
it now has 220 
