instincts 
i would have made more money if id invested it in a savings 
and loan at 5 percent he says with a grimace 
kauffman sold part interest in the royals to memphis businessman 
avron fogelman in the early 1980s he discounts recent speculation 
about fogelmans realestate business and says the team wont be 
moved from kansas city 
it is secure now and it will be secure in the future he 
said 
